      "body" : "My preference is the solution in which CKeyStore doesn't have any critical section (it's moved up to CBasicKeyStore) and becomes just a pure interface (well, leaving AddKey() and GetPubKey() as the only non-pure virtual methods, so it's still an abstract class rather than an interface) with only CKey, CPubKey, CKeyID, CScript and CScriptID as dependencies. \r\nI implemented that prerequisite in #5251.\r\n\r\nAs said earlier, it would be would to rename Solver() since it is very different from script/standard::Solver.\r\n\r\nBike-shedding a little bit, I would also change the name of the implementation from SignatureCreator to TxSignatureCreator (IMO SignatureChecker shoud have been named TxSignatureChecker as well).\r\nand maybe BaseSignatureCreator to just SignatureCreator.\r\n",
